WRC, the official game of the World Rally Championship FIA, a title developed by Milestone and distributed by Black Bean Games, not only offers lovers of petrol and driving games are able to compete in the skin of WRC stars in all classes and cars of the 2010 season, but also provides exclusive content to further expand their garages.

Discover the fastest rally cars, powerful and sophisticated ever created: Peugeot 205 T 16, Lancia Delta S4, Ford RS200, TC BX4 Citroen and Renault R5 Maxi Turbo. Each of these cars have two different external factors, making a total of ten designs. The sheer power of these beasts, of infamy in the history of rallying, will enrich the list of 18 official cars Black Bean Games offered in the basic package.
